I '''Andrea Levy''' (born 1956)<ref>Andrea Levy, [http://books.guardian.co.uk/departments/politicsphilosophyandsociety/story/0,6000,138282,00.html "This is my England", ''The Guardian'', February 19, 2000.]</ref> metung yang talasulat a Britanico, a mibait king[[London]] kareng pengari ibat [[Jamaica]], a miglayag papunta king Inglaterra o England king ''[[Empire Windrush]]'' aniang 1948.

I Levy keraklan lahi yang [[Jamaicans of African ancestry|Afro-Jamaican]]. Hudio ya ing ingkung na kang tata na, at ibat ne man Escocia (Scotland) i ingkung na king tud kang ima na..<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2000/feb/19/society1]</ref>

Migumpisa yang susulat i Levy aniang maigit neng treinta, oneng mepansin yang tambing ing mumuna nang novela, ing semi-autobiographical (mibasi ya king bie na ing metung nang dake) a  ''Every Light in the House Burnin'. '' Sinambut yang [[Whitbread Book Awards | Whitbread Book of the Year]] ing kapat nang novela, ing ''Small Island'' (2004), [[Orange Prize for Fiction]], ampong [[Commonwealth Writers' Prize]]. Mipalage ne antimong drama king telebision, a pepalage ning BBC aniang Diciembre 2009.<ref>[http://www.andrealevy.co.uk]</ref>

Ing kalima nang novela,  ing "The Long Song" mibili ya king short-list para king 2010 [[Man Booker Prize]] for fiction.

== Librung sinulat ==

* ''Every Light in the House Burnin''' (1994)
* ''Never Far from Nowhere'' (1996)
* ''Fruit of the Lemon'' (1999)
* ''[[Small Island]]'', (2004), winner of the 2004 [[Orange Prize for Fiction]], 2004 [[Whitbread Book Awards|Whitbread Book of the Year]], and 2005 [[Commonwealth Writers Prize]]
* ''The Long Song'' (2010) shortlisted for the 2010 [[List_of_winners_and_shortlisted_authors_of_the_Booker_Prize_for_Fiction|Mann Booker Prize]]

